  "body": "### Problem description\r\n\r\nRight now each node has to subscribe to `RANDOM_SUBNETS_PER_VALIDATOR * validators` random (long lived) subnets. This results in significant bandwidth use for some nodes while other nodes may not follow this rule\r\n\r\n### Solution description\r\n\r\nEnforce all nodes to subscribe to `SUBNETS_PER_NODE` ~~random~~ deterministic subnets (2 for mainnet), this would distribute load to all beacon nodes\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\nSee https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/3312",
